title: The Fate Of Frenemies With Dr. Drew - Frenemies #14
description: On this final episode of Frenemies for 2020 Dr. Drew and his associate Dr. Mark Young join us for a little psychological analysis as we try and navigate the troubled friendship of Ethan & Trisha. Will they be able to find some understanding? Or is Frenemies done forever?
